Package org.dhbw.geo.database

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DBAction
    An action is a task which can be executed.
    DBActionBrightness Deprecated 
    DBActionMessage
    This action sends a message via the Short Message Service (SMS).
    DBActionNotification
    This action creates a push notification with a specific text.
    DBActionSimple
    This class is used for simple actions which just contain one setting which can only be turned on or off.
    DBActionSound
    This action sets the sound setting for a specific audio stream.
    DBCondition
    A condition is used to define whether the rule's actions shall be triggered or not.
    DBConditionFence
    A geofence condition is a set of geofences which are observed.
    DBConditionTime
    A time condition is a set of times or timeframes which are observed.
    DBFence
    A fence represents a specific geofence assigned to a fence condition.
    DBHelper
    The helper manages the connection to the sqlite database.
    DBObject
    Represents any database object of this application.
    DBRule
    A rule contains conditions and actions.
